notes: Match delayed due to rain, shortened to 33 overs a side.
G Mylvaganam and Saleem Raza 27, record ODI opening partnership for the United Arab Emirates.

milestones.description: Saleem Raza and Mylvaganam's 27-run partnership is UAE's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 26 between Poonawala and Azhar Saeed
Johanne Samarasekera and Dukanwala's 28-run partnership is UAE's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 13 between Johanne Samarasekera and Zarawani
Johanne Samarasekera has become the top wicket-taker for UAE in ODIs with 3 wickets, going past Sohail Butt's 2
This is the lowest match aggregate (221) involving teams Pakistan & U.A.E. in ODIs
Arshad Laeeq has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (5) for UAE, going past Azhar Saeed
